THAT'S how you start a show! LOVE Janelle Monae. Her band deserves credit for their incredible talent, as well.💕🤩🙌🏽🎙🎶

As for the audience, they should've stepped it up a notch, bc they DEFINITELY seemed dull. Gotta get hyped! IMO, considering the profession they're in, one might expect a little more from them. I know if I were at the Oscars I'd be overjoyed to be in the presence of such outstanding talent! IDC how many yrs they may have attended, it's an honor to be invited & should be treated as such. Again, just my opinion. It's okay if others disagree.😊
